name: Tank
description: A big guy with a kind heart who tries his best to absorb damage for his friends

name: Ranged
description: A long ranged assassin always waiting for someone to cross her line of sight

name: Support
description: A caretaker who gives his life for his teammates

name: Assassin
description: A blood thirsty killer who enjoys watching others beg for mercy

name: Wraith
description: Has a chance to abduct enemy units or deal massive damage to enemy hero

name: Fortress
description: Provides nearby allies with a bubble shield increasing their defenses and his own

name: Plague
description: Shoots a canister at an enemy leaving a toxic cloud behind

name: WeatherMan
description: Spawns a totem on an enemes which deals damage to anyone in range
